column15: Almost certain it is a resistor network. Interpreting the code: “R” for resistor; “56” are the significant digits and “2” are number of zeros that follow; so resistors values would be 5;6k. “J8” is for the number of resistors in the network; 8 resistors.
Same as RN1; but “J4” means 4 resistors in the network.
